results.deck: Former Illinois based game studio, best known for Crüe Ball, Surf Ninjas, and the NBA Street series. NuFX, Inc was acquired by EA in 2004 to become EA Chicago.
results.description: The mission statement listed on their old website reads: "To be a leading developer of compelling, high-quality and challenging gaming software that represented a superior value to publishers of video entertainment."
results.name: NuFX, Inc.
